  "description": "A hummingbird perches delicately on a slender, horizontal branch amidst a lush, out-of-focus background of vibrant green leaves. The hummingbird is captured in profile, showcasing its iridescent throat feathers, which appear a ruby red color. The bird's body is predominantly green, blending somewhat with the foliage. The branch is a muted gray-brown, contrasting with the vivid greens and reds. The background is a soft blur of green, creating a shallow depth of field that highlights the bird and branch. Sunlight filters through the leaves, creating subtle highlights and shadows.",
